com.aliyun.oss.model

类 ObjectMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aliyun.oss.model.ObjectMetadata
  • 直接已知子类:
    SelectObjectMetadata

    public class ObjectMetadata
extends Object
    OSS Object's metadata. It has the user's custom metadata, as well as some standard http headers sent to OSS, such as Content-Length, ETag, etc.

      • getUserMetadata

        public Map<String,String> getUserMetadata()

        Gets the user's custom metadata.

        The custom metadata would be appended with x-oss-meta- in the request to OSS. But here the caller should not use x-oss-meta- as the prefix for the keys of the Map instance returned. Meanwhile，the keys is case insenstive and all keys returned from OSS server is in lower case.

        返回:
        User's custom metadata.
